body_html:
Bazel version: Build label: 0.4.4
I was able to push the apk by following the readme:
adb install -r bazel-bin/tensorflow/examples/android/tensorflow_demo.apk

But when I open the project in Android Studio it gives me only that error.
Event log gives only:
Error during Sync: Remote object doesn't exist!

body:
Bazel version: Build label: 0.4.4
I was able to push the apk by following the readme:
`adb install -r bazel-bin/tensorflow/examples/android/tensorflow_demo.apk`

But when I open the project in Android Studio it gives me only that error.
Event log gives only: 
`Error during Sync: Remote object doesn't exist!`
